<p begin="22811600000t" end="22845600000t" region="region.after" style="style.center" xml:id="subtitle547">Kerja lama di sini. Saya<br/>baru naikkan gaji awak RM50 tempoh hari.</p>
<p begin="22850800000t" end="22890800000t" region="region.after" style="style.center" xml:id="subtitle548">Apa yang susah sangat?<br/>Sudah ada gaji, menyimpanlah sedikit.</p>
<p begin="22891600000t" end="22908400000t" region="region.after" style="style.center" xml:id="subtitle549">Lelaki apa kalau tiada kereta?</p>
<p begin="22909200000t" end="22927600000t" region="region.after" style="style.center" xml:id="subtitle550">Muka sahaja ganas.</p>
<p begin="22932000000t" end="22943200000t" region="region.after" style="style.center" xml:id="subtitle551">Dah! Pergi!</p>
<p begin="22951600000t" end="22977600000t" region="region.after" style="style.center" xml:id="subtitle552">Inilah budak-budak sekarang.<br/>Tak pandai simpan duit.</p>
<p begin="22978400000t" end="22988800000t" region="region.after" style="style.center" xml:id="subtitle553">Boros.</p>
<p begin="23002400000t" end="23033200000t" region="region.after" style="style.center" xml:id="subtitle554">Mana pula saya nak cari rim baru untuk<br/>tukar?</p>
<p begin="23052000000t" end="23069600000t" region="region.after" style="style.center" xml:id="subtitle555">Kenapa nak tukar rim?</p>
<p begin="23080400000t" end="23117600000t" region="region.after" style="style.center" xml:id="subtitle556">Daripada tukar itu, baik saya tukar<br/>kereta sahaja. Lagi senang.</p>
