<p begin="23165600000t" end="23185600000t" region="region.after" style="style.center" xml:id="subtitle558">Banyak pula duit dia ini.</p>
<p begin="23200000000t" end="23212400000t" region="region.after" style="style.center" xml:id="subtitle559">Mana dia dapat ini?</p>
